A few of my friends love this as a mother's milk clone. &#xD;
I don't like strawberry and cream but can appreciate the mix.&#xD;
Strawberry Ripe % is really high. &#xD;
Mixed at 10% once and that was enough flavor for my personal tastes.&#xD;
YMMV. Gets a lot better the longer it steeps.
